reviewText: Rhea of Sun Books was very professional and  courteous. The DVD is full of useful information on the basics needed to conduct and participate in  a meeting. I would recommend it to anyone serving as a  parliamentarian, board member, or interested member of a society/club. Again, top notch service and product!
great for help doing trainings for executive board members.  office staff was very helpful with the supporting documents.  highly recommend using this when needed.
